libcamera (0.4.0-6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Make libcamera-tools depends on libcamera-ipa because libcamerify
    requires v4l2-compat.so to work.
  * Use libexec/${DEB_HOST_MULTIARCH} to override --libexecdir,
    otherwise v4l2-compat.so ends up in the same folder as IPA modules
    and IPA manager tries to parse it leading to errors.

